Package edu.ncsu.csc216.ticket_manager.model.manager

Class TicketManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.ticket_manager.model.manager.TicketManager
  • public class TicketManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for adding and removing tickets from TicketManager. Allows users to save and load Ticket lists, as well as execute commands on them to change states.
    Author:
    Benson Liu
